OL,3,CCouncil threatens #100 fines for
OL,4,Cswearing in public after beach fights
OL,6,FFines of #100 for swearing in public
OL,7,Fare among measures that have been
OL,8,Fapproved by a council in Kent as it
OL,9,Fattempts to crack down on public
OL,10,Fdisorder.
OL,12,FIt follows a series of beach brawls
OL,13,Fand attacks on Thanet town centre.
OL,15,FCouncillors at Thanet Council have now
OL,16,Fapproved a PSPO - a Public Spaces
OL,17,FProtection Order.
