OL,6,FLabour councillor Heather Keen said:
OL,7,F"The importance of the PSPO, which has
OL,8,Fseven behaviours identified, has been
OL,9,Fovershadowed by the portrayal that
OL,10,FThanet is banning swearing.
OL,12,F"This is a disingenuous, inaccurate
OL,13,Fheadline designed to grab attention.
OL,14,FLet me be clear, Thanet is not banning
OL,15,Fswearing or preventing free speech.
OL,17,F"The reference to foul and abusive
OL,18,Flanguage only applies if it is causing
OL,19,Fharassment, alarm or distress to
OL,20,Fanother person ` not if it is casual
OL,21,Fswearing."
