OL,6,FAn order was first brought in by
OL,7,FThanet in 2018, and similar orders
OL,8,Fexist in Canterbury and Dartford as
OL,9,Fwell as elsewhere in the country, the
OL,10,Fmeeting heard.
OL,12,FLast summer, when the council
OL,13,Fattempted to renew and reword their
OL,14,FPSPO, the proposal was rejected amid a
OL,15,Fthreat of a legal challenge.
OL,17,FThey said that more work has been
OL,18,Fundertaken to ensure this is something
OL,19,Ftheir residents want.
