OL,6,FWithin the report, the authors touch
OL,7,Fon concerns raised by Thanet
OL,8,Fresidents, who said the current
OL,9,Fwording was too broad and may lead to
OL,10,Fyoung people and people from minority
OL,11,Fbackgrounds being unfairly moved on or
OL,12,Ffined.
OL,14,FThere was also a concern that "causing
OL,15,Fdistress to others" could be used to
OL,16,Ftarget peaceful protests.
