OL,6,FCllr Heather Keen, Cabinet Member for
OL,7,FCommunities at Thanet District
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "We've listened, and
OL,9,Fthese measures are designed to
OL,10,Freassure residents and set clear
OL,11,Fexpectations around acceptable public
OL,12,Fbehaviour in Thanet.
OL,14,F"It crucially provides us with the
OL,15,Ftools to intervene earlier which we
OL,16,Fhope will successfully prevent
OL,17,Fsituations from escalating.
