OL,4,Cswearing in public after beach fights
OL,6,F"The overwhelming support from local
OL,7,Fpeople, businesses and the police
OL,8,Fduring the consultation process is
OL,9,Fevidence that these measures are
OL,10,Fwelcomed.
OL,12,F"Every year our residents tell us
OL,13,Ffeeling safe is a top priority.
OL,15,F"I'm proud to say that we've listened
OL,16,Fand hope this serves as a reminder
OL,17,Fthat antisocial behaviour will not be
OL,18,Ftolerated in Thanet."
